This is most helpful information.

Are you able to resend the orders made this year on the TA shop to me - unfortunately the link below isn't working for me.

Thanks

Julie

Thanks for your email.

Upon review, it appears the order was placed through a different website. Just to clarify, we don’t have access or manage the pedalmafia.cc.

We could resent the following orders from the below:
